description: Sanatana Resources Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. It explores for copper and gold. The company was formerly known as Sanatana Diamonds Inc. and changed its name to Sanatana Resources Inc. in April 2011. Sanatana Resources Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Peter Leighton Miles B.Com., B.Comm
